    <segment id="82">039;Tomie Dançante&amp;#039</segment>
    <segment id="83">;, no Instituto Tomie Ohtake - DivulgaçãoRumores Janja é dona de si.</segment>
    <segment id="84">Ela e eu.</segment>
    <segment id="85">Quer sumir das redes</segment>
    <segment id="86">, some.</segment>
